{"tid":1021440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[25仔]瑞典大使被指安排桂民海女兒與中國商人見面接受內部調查","createTime":"2019-02-14T09:03:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T17:59:34.000Z","uid":51271,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c2ed8e2035f63d9f1b45537034f63946dfa7f4b7","tid":1021440,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:03:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1067396&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1067396%26csid%3D261_341&d=ZfEq%2Fo1sgt4RLlfWMFNbDsdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=d9a9bf15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1067396&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正在內地被扣留的銅鑼灣書店店主桂民海，他的女兒Angela在網上發文，指瑞典駐華大使林戴安上月聯絡她，安排她與兩名中國商人在斯德哥爾摩一間酒店見面，中國商人要求她將所知的一切講出來，否則她不能再與父親見面，又警告她如果向傳媒發聲，會損害林戴安的仕途。<br />\n<br />\nAngela其後聯絡瑞典外交部，外交部回覆指對會面完全不知情。瑞典駐華大使館今日表示，大使林戴安正接受內部調查，昨日離開北京，飛回斯德哥爾摩會見外交部官員，但並非刑事調查。<br />\n<br />\nAngela全文:<br />\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/@angela_62804/damned-if-you-do-damned-if-you-dont-i-wont-1a09ba853018\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2F%40angela_62804%2Fdamned-if-you-do-damned-if-you-dont-i-wont-1a09ba853018&d=ZfEq%2Fo1sgt4RLlfWMFNbDsdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=a3329d7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://medium.com/@angela_62804/damned-if-you-do-damned-if-you-dont-i-wont-1a09ba853018</a>"},{"pid":"6947a2e1700120f91651f4add276ff3dbcfbc2c4","tid":1021440,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T09:58:19.000Z","msg":"又捉到一隻共諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n習囝又少一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知爆血管未<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99b739ac587bcd532c582de23d446d39a207dc22","tid":1021440,"uid":48083,"like":7,"dislik